Another satellite of Jupiter is announced, S/2017 J 1, just 3 days after the announcement of S/2016 J 1. (Minor Planet Center)The United Kingdom, on Friday, did not derive energy from any coal-fired source, the first continuous 24-hour, coal-free period for the UK since use of the fossil fuel began. Coal accounted for just 9 percent of the electricity generated last year. (Sky News)